###########################
### modest package news ###
###########################

Please report bugs and unexpected behaviour to Philip Pallmann <p.pallmann@lancaster.ac.uk>

#########################

Version 0.3-1 (3 November 2017)

- Minor change to simulations plot.
- Removed 'DT' from Imports.
- Removed MathJax elements.
- Updated maintainer email address.

#########################

Version 0.3 (26 September 2017)

- 'Show another run' button to generate multiple simulated examples.
- Download button for detailed simulation results in a csv file.
- Minor changes to the appearance of various graphs.

#########################

Version 0.2 (4 August 2017)

- New spreadsheet interface for manual data entry into 'Design' module.
- Informative error messages added.
- Pointwise 95% confidence bands added to dose-toxicity curves.
- New stopping rule based on the number of consecutive patients receiving the same dose.
- Two vignettes added.
- Various minor bug fixes and improvements.

#########################

Version 0.1 (26 June 2017)

- Initial release.